Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:18.42,0:53:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又看我打手枪吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:25.49,0:53:30.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好唷 看着我打手枪吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:32.96,0:53:37.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,握着肉棒好爽吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:40.97,0:53:47.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,边看我脸边打手枪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:53:55.92,0:53:58.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也想亲亲？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:00.19,0:54:03.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等再亲喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:15.81,0:54:22.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊 想被摸哪啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:24.08,0:54:25.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:30.35,0:54:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己说看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:33.96,0:54:36.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听不到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:37.69,0:54:39.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:41.16,0:54:43.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:45.97,0:54:52.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒啊变大的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:52.24,0:54:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮你摩擦唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:54:57.18,0:55:01.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变大了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:03.32,0:55:06.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,确认好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:13.33,0:55:18.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肉棒子 变硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:20.14,0:55:23.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好下流喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:31.75,0:55:34.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何变硬了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:38.15,0:55:42.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幻想做爱吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:55:54.70,0:55:58.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先从内裤外喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:01.91,0:56:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淫汁让内裤湿了直接摸唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:14.72,0:56:21.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流更多吧 淫汁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:27.80,0:56:31.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顶到了？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:35.15,0:56:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你肉棒被我奶子顶到？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:43.95,0:56:49.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好清楚唷 肉棒顶着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:56:58.50,0:57:02.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好硬好热
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:12.52,0:57:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:24.39,0:57:28.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:28.40,0:57:31.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这边也硬了唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:34.40,0:57:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶头也敏感吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:57:44.15,0:57:48.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用嘴舔好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:12.98,0:58:15.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:36.20,0:58:40.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左右哪粒奶头敏感？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:58:44.61,0:58:47.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,换这粒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:14.24,0:59:16.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,左边比较敏感吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:19.44,0:59:22.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬硬的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:26.92,0:59:30.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶头也好下流
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:34.92,0:59:41.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悟想看我小奶子？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:45.34,0:59:48.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说想看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:59:55.61,0:59:59.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只给你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:09.63,1:00:14.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悟 看吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:15.63,1:00:18.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我小奶子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:21.50,1:00:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶头如何·
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:26.04,1:00:28.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:32.98,1:00:38.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悟摸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:40.99,1:00:43.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我小奶子
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:44.06,1:00:47.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,摸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:00:58.07,1:01:02.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悟再用力
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:13.29,1:01:17.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奶头好硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:30.37,1:01:32.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:40.38,1:01:44.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我小奶子如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:45.19,1:01:48.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小但软吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:54.13,1:01:59.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的 肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:01:59.87,1:02:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相反耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:04.41,1:02:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬又大
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:16.82,1:02:20.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掏出来好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:20.29,1:02:25.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:02:49.39,1:02:53.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变好大
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:04.07,1:03:06.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有味道
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:13.94,1:03:16.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舔好吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:34.76,1:03:37.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,流淫汁了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:03:42.91,1:03:47.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好咸
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:01.59,1:04:05.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:04:39.76,1:04:44.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我嘴里爽？·
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:05.26,1:05:11.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用我的嘴 好好爽唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:36.09,1:05:39.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,更硬了耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:05:42.76,1:05:46.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前端爽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:01.04,1:06:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前端爽吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:24.67,1:06:28.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然这爽啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:32.28,1:06:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好刺激这唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:37.88,1:06:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好地爽唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:53.36,1:06:56.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悟爽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:06:58.70,1:07:04.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒 硬邦邦唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:15.39,1:07:20.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬邦邦肉棒很色唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:33.54,1:07:37.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小悟爽？
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:51.69,1:07:54.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要射吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:07:55.16,1:07:58.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好唷射唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:03.83,1:08:07.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再射很多
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:16.51,1:08:21.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好湿
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:38.54,1:08:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:08:49.35,1:08:55.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射好多浓浓的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:00.69,1:09:02.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:12.44,1:09:16.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又流了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:19.64,1:09:21.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,积很久吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:24.71,1:09:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爽吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:09:31.52,1:09:37.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再 做更多色色的事唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:18.50,1:10:23.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这 为何
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:24.64,1:10:28.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为何在我家
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:40.79,1:10:47.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她来 见我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:10:53.60,1:10:59.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,受不了来见我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:03.88,1:11:09.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也喜欢你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:09.22,1:11:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,马上去见你等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:23.10,1:11:26.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越来越有人气耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:26.17,1:11:32.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没这回事但很努力温泉外景的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:32.98,1:11:34.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,场景
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:35.25,1:11:37.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我会加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:41.92,1:11:43.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天八点
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:11:43.65,1:11:47.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是拜托了辛苦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:17.75,1:13:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:13:28.43,1:13:30.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:16:13.12,1:16:16.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢你唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:06.13,1:24:11.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你今天来见我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:11.47,1:24:18.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你喜欢我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:24:22.28,1:24:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也喜欢·
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:01.36,1:29:04.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:06.03,1:29:09.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:11.10,1:29:14.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己打开
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:19.11,1:29:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:29:30.19,1:29:36.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想看小穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:27.31,1:30:29.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:33.32,1:30:36.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,脚打开
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:38.92,1:30:41.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:30:46.26,1:30:49.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再打开
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:31:01.88,1:31:04.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:38:50.61,1:38:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舔啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:30.05,1:40:33.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舔出声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:40:42.99,1:40:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,最喜欢你唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:00.80,1:42:03.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:42:04.14,1:42:08.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再再再看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:47:22.86,1:47:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再插唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:55:21.60,1:55:23.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打开
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:57:19.32,1:57:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,射
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:37.80,1:58:41.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我爱你唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:58:41.54,1:58:45.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是我的
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:27.58,1:59:32.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小枫有现场的事想问你
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:36.13,1:59:37.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小枫
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:37.59,1:59:40.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真啰嗦耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:40.40,1:59:43.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:43.33,1:59:45.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,放过我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:46.94,1:59:51.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全没听进去
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:54.68,1:59:59.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想但
Dialogue: Marked=0,1:59:59.22,2:00:02.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的懂吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:02.55,2:00:07.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老是脏脏的让人难受
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:07.36,2:00:12.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我出错的话你要负责吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:14.03,2:00:17.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不敢吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:20.17,2:00:25.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,老是浑身汗臭真让人难受
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:28.98,2:00:30.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:00:31.11,2:00:32.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失礼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:07.95,2:01:10.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可恶 贱女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:10.89,2:01:15.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一副了不起的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:01:18.90,2:01:24.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对让你后悔
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:34.70,2:02:37.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很清楚嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:37.51,2:02:40.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍到了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:40.98,2:02:44.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怎么办呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:44.71,2:02:49.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1、放网络上
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:50.05,2:02:54.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2、卖给杂志
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:54.46,2:02:57.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3、给狂热者
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:02:58.06,2:03:05.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4、给人看当白痴
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:03:07.40,2:03:11.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪个好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:05:17.13,2:05:21.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谁 住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:16:04.85,2:16:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:16:15.53,2:16:18.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小枫\N是
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:16:18.33,2:16:19.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:16:21.80,2:16:23.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:16:25.67,2:16:28.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:16:39.28,2:16:41.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:16:45.56,2:16:51.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才想问啊怎么回事啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:16:55.83,2:17:01.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你啊什么私生活我不想问
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:01.70,2:17:06.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但这到底是什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:09.18,2:17:13.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是我的错吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:13.45,2:17:19.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人气女优 我太高兴了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:19.72,2:17:23.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以才变这样子吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:23.99,2:17:30.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样我们的名誉破产了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:34.00,2:17:36.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:44.81,2:17:48.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说啊这淫乱女
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:17:51.76,2:17:55.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:18:00.96,2:18:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是你的错吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:18:04.03,2:18:11.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一般大事务所都会花钱处理吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:18:11.64,2:18:14.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会舍得花钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:18:14.98,2:18:17.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:18:26.86,2:18:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小气公司连钱都舍不得花
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:18:31.93,2:18:35.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:18:36.07,2:18:40.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘记是我提拔你吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:18:41.00,2:18:43.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,提拔？
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:18:43.27,2:18:48.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么小的事务所谁稀罕啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:18:48.75,2:18:52.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上没人看的白痴节目
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:18:52.88,2:18:54.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:19:18.64,2:19:22.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那天后几个礼拜
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:19:22.65,2:19:28.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就没去公司了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:19:28.52,2:19:31.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也面试了几家公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:19:31.45,2:19:35.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全部没下文
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:19:36.93,2:19:42.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往后我没有报导工作了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:19:44.67,2:19:51.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那件事让我照片被散播出去
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:19:51.88,2:19:58.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,散播照片的是那男人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:20:16.57,2:20:19.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公司怎样我不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:20:19.50,2:20:25.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社长到员工都没跟我联络
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:20:51.40,2:20:54.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小枫
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:20:57.01,2:20:59.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,社长
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:21:02.21,2:21:05.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,托小枫的福
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:21:05.42,2:21:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公司倒了唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:21:09.69,2:21:13.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:21:13.42,2:21:19.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但那公司
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:21:19.70,2:21:25.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有小枫也做不了什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:21:28.24,2:21:31.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公司倒闭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:21:32.11,2:21:35.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想到好点子
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:21:41.32,2:21:43.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:21:43.99,2:21:47.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍你淫荡就好了嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:21:47.46,2:21:50.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说什么啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:21:50.93,2:21:54.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你粉丝也会开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:22:01.34,2:22:04.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:22:42.85,2:22:45.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:23:04.87,2:23:09.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我当副社长了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:23:09.81,2:23:12.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,升官了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:25:30.08,2:25:33.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:27:37.14,2:27:39.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:29:35.93,2:29:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:47:06.84,2:47:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:47:09.25,2:47:13.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要 住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:58:11.91,2:58:16.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拍到了吗？\N拍了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:58:18.45,2:58:21.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说拍到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:58:21.79,2:58:27.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,往后啊 一起工作请多指教唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:58:27.26,2:58:30.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做好作品唷
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:58:32.46,2:58:37.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,彼此彼此啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,2:58:55.29,2:59:01.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完
